quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,64,"Kaa ko hommbo fu…ó…óii tagu ngun ka rennga laawol …ìaawo laawol, refti O wurnita ngu …ìaawo O warii ngu, e ko hommbo kadi arsikata on immorde ka kammu to…ìo saa∆¥oowo iwrungo e maggu, O arsika on kadi immorde ka leydi pu…ói …ói O fu…óinta …óin e nder mayri! Enee, ko rewetee…óo goo woni wa…óude …óum wonndude e Alla?! Maakan -an Nulaa…óo- …ìee sirkoo…ìe: Addee hujja moo…óon on e dow ko wonu- …óon kon e muu…óum immorde e sirku, si tawii on wonii goongu …ìe e ko nodditi…óon kon wonndema hi…óon e hoore goonga."
  27,65,"Maaku -an Nulaa…óo-: Anndaa ko wirnii kon …ìen wonu…ìe ka kammuuli immorde e Malaa'ika en, wanaa …ìen wonu…ìe ka leydi kadi immorde e yim…ìe …ìen, kono ko Alla tun woni Anndu…óo …óum, dennda- ngal …ìen wonu…ìe ka kammuuli e …ìen won…ìe ka leydi …ìe anndaa ko hennde tuma …ìe immintinoytee fii njo…ìdi ndin, si wanaa Alla."
  27,66,"Kaa hara ganndal ma…ì…ìe jokkondir fii Laakara on …ìe yananaa fii makko? Oo'ooye, ko woni, kam…ìe hi…ìe e sikke e wemmbere fii Laakara on, wurin gom…óii gite ma…ì…ìe …óen wumii gaayi [Laakara on]."
  27,67,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe wi'i e hoore mawnitagol: Enee, si men maayii men woni mbullaari no wee…ìi nde men immintinoytee hara ko men wuuru…ìe?"
  27,68,"Gom…óii men fodanooma, baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen kadi fodaa ko adii wonndema men fow men immintinoyte, kono men yi'aali nden fodoore no laatii, ndee fodoore nde men fow men fodaa wonaali si wonaa pene adinoo…ìe …ìen …óe …ìe winndunoo …óen ka defte ma…ì…ìe."
  27,69,"An Nulaa…óo maakan …ìen yeddu…ìe Immital ngal: Yahee e kala …ìa≈ã≈ãeeji leydi ndin tasko…óon ko honno wonirnoo lannoode bon…ìe fennu…ìe …ìen Immital ngal, gom…óii Men halkii …ìe sabu fennugol ma…ì…ìe ngol Immital ngal."
  27,70,"Wata a suno sabu …óuuragol sirkoo…ìe …ìen gaayi noddaandu maa…óa ndun, wata pewje ma…ì…ìe …óen …ìittin …ìernde maa…óa nden Alla wallete e hoore ma…ì…ìe."
  27,71,"Heefer…ìe yeddu…ìe Immital jeyaa…ìe e yim…ìe maa…óa …ìen no wi'ude: "Ko honnde tuma Lepte …óe fodu…óaa men …óen an e gom…óin…ìe …ìen laatotoo, si tawii ko on goongu…ìe e kon ko nodditi…óon wa…óugol mum."
  27,72,"Maakan …ìe -an Nulaa…óo-: No tijjaa nde tawata …ìadanike on yoga e ko he√±or…óon kon immorde e Lepte …óen."
  27,73,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- ko O Jom ∆Åural e dow yim…ìe …ìen nokku O accata he√±orgol leptugol …ìe wonndude e keefeeru e geddi …ói …ìe woni …óin e moo…óun, kono …ìur…ìe heewude …ìen e yim…ìe …ìen …ìe jarnataa Alla e dow ko O neeminiri …ìe kon."
  27,74,"Pellet Joomi maa…óa hiMo Anndi ko …ìer…óe jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen miijotoo e ko …óe fe√±√±inta kon, hay e huunde e …óum suu…óotaako Mo, aray O yo…ìa …ìe e dow …óum."
  27,75,"Alaa e huunde wirniinde e gite yim…ìe …ìen ka kammu, wanaa kadi wirniinde e ma…ì…ìe ka leydi, si wanaa nden huunde wonii e nder Deftere …ìanngunde, …óum le ko Alluwal Reenaangal ngal."
  27,76,"Pellet, ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) hinde filloo e dow …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen ko …ìuri heewunde e ko …ìe luutondiri kon e fii mu'un, hinde hunca kadi …ìoylaare ma…ì…ìe nden."